<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NEXUS</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="./assets/logo.svg" type="image/x-icon">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@24,400,0,0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/postPage.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="directory">
        <div class="logo-directory">
            <a href=""><img class="logo-top" src="./assets/logo.svg"></a>
            <p>Home/PostPage</p>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="settings"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">power_settings_new</span></a>
    </div>
    <div class="sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-no-settings">
            <a href="/studentHomePage" class="icon-link open"><img class="home icon" src="/assets/home.png"></a>
            <a href="/searchpage" class="icon-link"><img class="search-icon icon"  src="/assets/search.png"></a>
            <a href="/hirePage" class="icon-link"><img class="search-icon icon" src="/assets/job-icon.png"></a>
            <a href="/notificationPage" class="icon-link"><img class="notifications icon"  src="/assets/bell.png"></a>
            <a href="/collabPage" class="icon-link"><img class="users icon"  src="/assets/users.png"></a>
            <a href="/messagePage" class="icon-link"><img class="messages icon"  src="/assets/send.png"></a>
            <a href="/profilePage" class="icon-link "><img class="profile icon"  src="/assets/profile.png"></a> 
        </div>        
    </div>
    <div class="popup-container" id="popup-container">
        <div class="popup" id="popup">
            <h2>Settings</h2>
            <p>This is the settings popup.</p>
            <button id="close-popup">Close</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="main-container">
        <div class="post">
            <div class="head">
                <div class="details">
                    <div  class="image">
                        <img id="user-profile" src="./assets/profile-pic2.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="name">Hemanth</div>
                </div>
                <!-- <div class="follow"><i class="fa-thin fa-plus icon">&nbsp <span>Follow</i></div>  -->
            </div>

            <div class="content">
                <img src="./assets/p1.png" alt="Amazon Page">
            </div>
            <div class="features">
                <div class="controls">
                    <button class="f-icons like-btn"><i class="fa-regular fa-heart"></i></button>
                    <button class="f-icons save-btn"><i class="fa-regular fa-bookmark"></i></button>
                    <a href="#post-comment"><button class="f-icons comment-btn"><i class="fa-regular fa-comment"></i></button></a>
                </div>
                <div class="desc title">
                    <h4 class="project-name">Amazon Tool Kit</h4>
                    <div class="description">Description</div>
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Exercitationem dolorem accusantium fugit nobis consequatur repellat voluptatum beatae similique recusandae, blanditiis culpa sint laboriosam ullam harum ipsam quibusdam dicta quia earum commodi quos! Eius sit harum repudiandae libero laboriosam dolorem quos.</p>
                </div> 
            </div>
            <div class="post-comment" id="post-comment">
                <div class="head">
                    <div class="name">
                        Comments
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="comments">
                    <div class="comment">
                        <img src="./assets/profile-pic.jpeg" alt="">
                        <div class="comment-text">
                            Implement a basic
                            calculator application with a clean User Interface of your choice based on
                            following the MVC framework design pattern and involving EJS concept.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="comment">
                        <img src="./assets/profile-pic2.png" alt="">
                        <div class="comment-text">Implement a basic
                            calculator application with a clean User Interface of your choice based on
                            following the MVC framework design pattern and involving EJS concept.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="comment">
                        <img src="./assets/profile-pic2.png" alt="">
                        <div class="comment-text">Implement a basic
                            calculator application with a clean User Interface of your choice based on
                            following the MVC framework design pattern and involving EJS concept.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    
                </div>
                <div class="new-comment">
                    <div class="new-comment-details">
                        <img src="./assets/profile-pic2.png" alt=""/>
                        <input id="input-comment" type="text" placeholder="Add a Comment...."/>
                    </div>
                    <button id="send-comment"><i class="fa-regular fa-paper-plane"></i></button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="./js/postPage.js"></script>
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/6953004357.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>